N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 19 ยง 131.2 - Fee

State Regulations

The fee for filing a registration of a person claiming to
be a successor in interest to the rights of a deceased personality or a
licensee thereof with the Department of State under Civil Rights Law Section
50-f is one hundred fifty dollars. Notes
